4
00:00:11,633 --> 00:00:14,500
I hope there are some
good looking male patients.

5
00:00:14,600 --> 00:00:18,600
What if I fall in love
with one of them?

6
00:00:18,700 --> 00:00:19,700
Hurry!

7
00:00:22,867 --> 00:00:27,833
<i>At last! I wonder what kind</i>
<i>of patients we'll get!</i>

8
00:00:29,033 --> 00:00:31,900
I want Nurse Kotoko!

9
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:33,633
Leave it to me!

10
00:00:34,100 --> 00:00:36,900
Naotaro, you have to cooperate.

11
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:40,100
But I... I...

12
00:00:42,367 --> 00:00:43,633
Sounds good.

13
00:00:46,733 --> 00:00:47,933
My...

14
00:00:50,567 --> 00:00:52,900
You're like a granddaughter to me.

15
00:00:54,533 --> 00:00:57,733
Oh, Grandma Naoko.

16
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:02,567
But it can't all be so good.

17
00:01:05,100 --> 00:01:07,167
