19
00:01:15,433 --> 00:01:16,367
Stupid!

20
00:01:16,800 --> 00:01:20,533
Weakling! I know you can do it!

21
00:01:21,800 --> 00:01:23,100
Nurse Kotoko...

22
00:01:24,367 --> 00:01:26,467
We'll work hard...together.

23
00:01:33,533 --> 00:01:36,600
Kotoko is in dreamland again.

24
00:01:37,967 --> 00:01:41,300
Hey, Irie! Come back!

25
00:01:44,533 --> 00:01:45,533
I'm sorry...

26
00:01:45,600 --> 00:01:48,700
No daydreaming during training.

27
00:01:49,167 --> 00:01:50,067
Yes.

28
00:01:50,133 --> 00:01:53,767
The printouts I gave you
outline the case histories

29
00:01:53,867 --> 00:01:57,867
of patients in the orthopedic department
to which you are assigned.

30
00:01:59,300 --> 00:02:00,667
Read them over carefully

31
00:02:01,167 --> 00:02:03,567
so you can manage them properly.

32
00:02:04,333 --> 00:02:05,600
Yes!

33
00:03:58,767 --> 00:04:00,933
